<paragraph blockId="17.[151,1436,222,463]" pageId="17" pageNumber="328">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,387,402,427]" pageId="17" pageNumber="328">Biological notes</emphasis>
. Only one male specimen (
<typeStatus box="[701,802,402,427]" pageId="17" pageNumber="328">holotype</typeStatus>
) has been found from the Andean-Amazonian interface in southern 
<collectingCountry box="[283,338,439,462]" name="Peru" pageId="17" pageNumber="328">Peru</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
